>Construction of pLYC9
acquire oligo ZH9			
acquire oligo ZH9R
acquire oligo ZH5
acquire oligo ZH5R
acquire oligo ZH10
acquire oligo ZH10R
acquire plasmid pLYC5
acquire plasmid pAtipiTrc
PCR ZH9,ZH5R on pLYC5 (2172 bp, pcrA)
PCR ZH5,ZH10R on pLYC5 (4727 bp, pcrB)
PCR ZH10,ZH9R on pAtipiTrc (1061 bp, pcrC)
Assemble pcrA,pcrB,pcrC	(Gibson, pLYC9)
Transform pLYC9	(Mach1, Amp)
